209" end="00:26.720">ideals,</span> <span begin="00:26.720" end="00:26.851">we</span> <span begin="00:26.851" end="00:27.208">shouldn't</span> <span begin="00:27.208" end="00:27.595">settle</span> <span begin="00:27.595" end="00:27.726">for</span> <span begin="00:27.726" end="00:28.171">less</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们曾为这些理想奋斗 我们不该退而求其次</span></p><p begin="00:28.311" end="00:31.163" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:28.311" end="00:28.668">These</span> <span begin="00:28.668" end="00:28.823">are</span> <span begin="00:28.823" end="00:29.162">wise</span> <span begin="00:29.162" end="00:29.519">words,</span> <span begin="00:29.519" end="00:30.340">enterprising</span> <span begin="00:30.340" end="00:30.619">men</span> <span begin="00:30.619" end="00:30.988">quote</span> <span begin="00:30.988" end="00:31.163">'em</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这些睿智之言 被有志之士引用</span></p><p begin="00:31.163" end="00:33.918" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:31.163" end="00:31.544">Don't</span> <span begin="00:31.544" end="00:31.764">act</span> <span begin="00:31.764" end="00:32.145">surprised,</span> <span begin="00:32.145" end="00:32.329">you</span> <span begin="00:32.329" end="00:32.686">guys,</span> <span begin="00:32.686" end="00:32.900">'cause</span> <span begin="00:32.900" end="00:33.198">I</span> <span begin="00:33.198" end="00:33.632">wrote</span> <span begin="00:33.632" end="00:33.918">'em</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不要惊讶 各位 因为这些出自我的笔下</span></p><p begin="00:34.141" end="00:36.289" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:34.141" end="00:35.087">Ow,</span> <span begin="00:35.087" end="00:35.283">but</span> <span begin="00:35.283" end="00:35.795">Hamilton</span> <span begin="00:35.795" end="00:36.289">forgets</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">哦 但汉密尔顿忘了</span></p><p begin="00:36.461" end="00:39.023" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:36.461" end="00:36.704">His</span> <span begin="00:36.704" end="00:36.947">plan</span> <span begin="00:36.947" end="00:37.047">would</span> <span begin="00:37.047" end="00:37.215">have</span> <span begin="00:37.215" end="00:37.370">the</span> <span begin="00:37.370" end="00:37.858">government</span> <span begin="00:37.858" end="00:38.316">assume</span> <span begin="00:38.316" end="00:38.768">state's</span> <span begin="00:38.768" end="00:39.023">debts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">他的计划是让政府承担各州的债务</span></p><p begin="00:39.282" end="00:41.709" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="00:39.282" end="00:39.590">Now,</span> <span begin="00:39.590" end="00:39.809">place</span> <span begin="00:39.809" end="00:40.043">your</span> <span begin="00:40.043" end="00:40.313">bets</span> <span begin="00:40.313" end="00:40.493">as</span> <span begin="00:40.493" end="00:40.654">to</span> <span begin="00:40.654" end="00:40.814">who</span> <span begin="00:40.814" end="00:41.034">that</span> <span begin="00:41.034" end="00:41.709">benefits</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">现在 各位猜猜谁会从中获益</span></p><p begin="00:41.992" end="00:45.117" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="00:41.992" end="00:42.226">The</span> <span begin="00:42.226" end="00:42.404">very</span> <span begin="00:42.404" end="00:42.636">seat</span> <span begin="00:42.636" end="00:42.809">of</span> <span begin="00:42.809" end="00:43.314">government</span> <span begin="00:43.314" end="00:43.534">where</span> <span begin="00:43.534" end="00:44.159">Hamilton</span> <span begin="00:44.159" end="00:45.117">sits</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">正是汉密尔顿所在的政府</span></p><p begin="00:44.443" end="00:45.451" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="00:44.443" end="00:44.871">Not</span> <span begin="00:44.871" end="00:45.451">true!</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不对啊</span></p><p begin="00:45.227" end="00:47.413" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="