:54.102" end="00:54.292">got</span> <span begin="00:54.292" end="00:54.465">it</span> <span begin="00:54.465" end="00:54.786">made</span> <span begin="00:54.786" end="00:54.911">in</span> <span begin="00:54.911" end="00:55.036">the</span> <span begin="00:55.036" end="00:55.665">shade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">别向南方征税 因为我们已经过得很舒服了</span></p><p begin="00:55.956" end="00:57.908" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="00:55.956" end="00:56.169">In</span> <span begin="00:56.169" end="00:56.484">Virginia,</span> <span begin="00:56.484" end="00:56.663">we</span> <span begin="00:56.663" end="00:56.948">plant</span> <span begin="00:56.948" end="00:57.341">seeds</span> <span begin="00:57.341" end="00:57.441">in</span> <span begin="00:57.441" end="00:57.573">the</span> <span begin="00:57.573" end="00:57.908">ground</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">弗吉尼亚人在自己的土地上播种</span></p><p begin="00:57.918" end="01:00.597" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="00:57.918" end="00:58.210">We</span> <span begin="00:58.210" end="00:58.670">create,</span> <span begin="00:58.799" end="00:58.947">you</span> <span begin="00:58.947" end="00:59.120">just</span> <span begin="00:59.120" end="00:59.429">wanna</span> <span begin="00:59.429" end="00:59.631">move</span> <span begin="00:59.631" end="00:59.840">our</span> <span begin="00:59.840" end="01:00.119">money</span> <span begin="01:00.119" end="01:00.597">around</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">而你只是想夺走我们的钱财</span></p><p begin="01:00.919" end="01:03.356" ttm:agent="v2" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="01:00.919" end="01:01.185">This</span> <span begin="01:01.185" end="01:01.887">financial</span> <span begin="01:01.887" end="01:02.184">plan</span> <span begin="01:02.184" end="01:02.309">is</span> <span begin="01:02.309" end="01:02.409">an</span> <span begin="01:02.409" end="01:03.041">outrageous</span> <span begin="01:03.041" end="01:03.356">demand</span><span ttm:role="x-tra